cs.CV, cs.IR, cs.MM, cs.DL, cs.HC. 

The paper proposes a manga-specific image retrieval system that uses efficient margin labeling, edge orientation histogram feature description, and approximate nearest-neighbor search. These techniques are commonly used in computer vision (cs.CV) and information retrieval (cs.IR) research. The paper also mentions the use of deep learning (cs.DL) for feature extraction, and the evaluation of the system's usability (cs.HC). Finally, the paper presents a novel dataset of manga images (cs.MM).
